import React from "react";
import styled from 'styled-components/native';

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Login1 className={props.className}>
      <LoginView>
        <Rectangle1></Rectangle1>
        <Account />
        <Account1 />
        <ForgotPasword>{`Quên mật khẩu?`}</ForgotPasword>
        <Button1>
          <Rectangle18></Rectangle18>
          <LoginRequest>{`Đăng nhập`}</LoginRequest>
        </Button1>
        <Frame38>
          <Frame5028>
            <LoginUsingGoogle>{`Đăng nhập bằng Google`}</LoginUsingGoogle>
          </Frame5028>
          <Way>{`Hoặc`}</Way>
          <Frame5029></Frame5029>
        </Frame38>
        <Image2 src={Image2Image} loading="lazy" alt={'image 2'} />
        <Frame50291></Frame50291>
        <Image3 src={Image3Image} loading="lazy" alt={'image 3'} />
        <AccountRequest>
          <AccountRequestSpan1>{`Bạn chưa có tài khoản ? `}</AccountRequestSpan1>
          <AccountRequestSpan2>{` Đăng kí ngay`}</AccountRequestSpan2>
          <AccountRequestSpan3>{` `}</AccountRequestSpan3>
        </AccountRequest>
      </LoginView>
    </Login1>
  );
};

const Login1 = styled('div')({
  backgroundImage: `url(${Login1Image})`,
  backgroundPosition: `center`,
  backgroundSize: `cover`,
  backgroundRepeat: `no-repeat`,
  border: `1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)`,
  boxSizing: `border-box`,
  borderRadius: `0px`,
  display: `flex`,
  position: `relative`,
  isolation: `isolate`,
  flexDirection: `row`,
  width: '100%',
  height: `1024px`,
  justifyContent: `flex-start`,
  alignItems: `flex-start`,
  padding: `0px`,
  overflow: `hidden`,
});

const LoginView = styled('div')({
  display: `flex`,
  position: `absolute`,
  isolation: `isolate`,
  flexDirection: `row`,
  justifyContent: `flex-start`,
  alignItems: `flex-start`,
  padding: `0px`,
  boxSizing: `border-box`,
  width: `528px`,
  height: `652px`,
  left: `456px`,
  top: `87px`,
});

const Rectangle1 = styled('div')({
  backgroundColor: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)`,
  borderRadius: `20px`,
  width: `528px`,
  height: `652px`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `0px`,
  top: `0px`,
});

const Account = styled(Group54)(({ theme }) => ({
  width: `451px`,
  height: `92px`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `35px`,
  top: `291px`,
}));

const Account1 = styled(Group54)(({ theme }) => ({
  width: `451px`,
  height: `92px`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `35px`,
  top: `410px`,
}));

const ForgotPasword = styled('div')({
  textAlign: `left`,
  whiteSpace: `pre-wrap`,
  fontSynthesis: `none`,
  color: `rgba(27, 106, 170, 1)`,
  fontStyle: `normal`,
  fontFamily: `Nunito`,
  fontWeight: `500`,
  fontSize: `18px`,
  letterSpacing: `0px`,
  textDecoration: `none`,
  textTransform: `none`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `194px`,
  top: `603px`,
});

const Button1 = styled('div')({
  display: `flex`,
  position: `absolute`,
  isolation: `isolate`,
  flexDirection: `row`,
  justifyContent: `flex-start`,
  alignItems: `flex-start`,
  padding: `0px`,
  boxSizing: `border-box`,
  width: `236px`,
  height: `54px`,
  left: `143px`,
  top: `529px`,
});

const Rectangle18 = styled('div')({
  backgroundColor: `rgba(27, 106, 170, 1)`,
  boxShadow: `0px 4px 19px rgba(119, 147, 65, 0.3)`,
  borderRadius: `10px`,
  width: `236px`,
  height: `54px`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `0px`,
  top: `0px`,
});

const LoginRequest = styled('div')({
  textAlign: `left`,
  whiteSpace: `pre-wrap`,
  fontSynthesis: `none`,
  color: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)`,
  fontStyle: `normal`,
  fontFamily: `Nunito`,
  fontWeight: `500`,
  fontSize: `18px`,
  letterSpacing: `0px`,
  textDecoration: `none`,
  textTransform: `none`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `76px`,
  top: `14px`,
});

const Frame38 = styled('div')({
  borderRadius: `0px`,

  position: `absolute`,
  isolation: `isolate`,
  flexDirection: `row`,
  justifyContent: `flex-start`,
  alignItems: `flex-start`,
  padding: `0px`,
  boxSizing: `border-box`,
  width: `297px`,
  height: `49px`,
  left: `106px`,
  top: `166px`,
});

const Frame5028 = styled('div')({
  borderRadius: `0px`,

  flexDirection: `row`,

  alignItems: `flex-start`,
  padding: `0px`,
  boxSizing: `border-box`,
  width: `297px`,
  height: `49px`,
  left: `0px`,
  top: `0px`,
  overflow: `hidden`,
});

const LoginUsingGoogle = styled('div')({
  textAlign: `left`,
  whiteSpace: `pre-wrap`,
  fontSynthesis: `none`,
  color: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)`,
  fontStyle: `normal`,
  fontFamily: `Poppins`,
  fontWeight: `400`,
  fontSize: `18px`,
  letterSpacing: `0px`,
  textDecoration: `none`,
  textTransform: `none`,

const Way = styled('div')({

  letterSpacing: `0px`,

});

const Frame5029 = styled('div')({
  border: `1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)`,
  boxSizing: `border-box`,
  borderRadius: `0px`,
  display: `flex`,
  position: `absolute`,
  isolation: `isolate`,
  flexDirection: `row`,
  justifyContent: `flex-start`,
  alignItems: `flex-start`,
  width: `205px`,
  height: `22px`,
  left: `128px`,
  top: `76px`,
  overflow: `hidden`,
});

const Image2 = styled('img')({
  height: `79px`,
  width: `80px`,
  objectFit: `cover`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `224px`,
  top: `23px`,
});

const Frame50291 = styled('div')({
  border: `1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)`,
  boxSizing: `border-box`,
  borderRadius: `0px`,
  display: `flex`,
  position: `absolute`,
  isolation: `isolate`,
  flexDirection: `row`,
  justifyContent: `flex-start`,
  alignItems: `flex-start`,
  width: `198px`,

  top: `242px`,

});

const Image3 = styled('img')({
  height: `60px`,
  width: `54px`,
  objectFit: `cover`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `107px`,
  top: `160px`,
});

const AccountRequestSpan1 = styled('span')({
  whiteSpace: `pre-wrap`,
  color: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)`,
  fontStyle: `normal`,
  fontFamily: `Poppins`,
  fontWeight: `400`,
  fontSize: `16px`,
  letterSpacing: `0px`,

  textTransform: `none`,
});

const AccountRequestSpan2 = styled('span')({
  whiteSpace: `pre-wrap`,
  color: `rgba(27, 106, 170, 1)`,
  fontStyle: `normal`,
  fontFamily: `Poppins`,
  fontWeight: `400`,

const AccountRequestSpan3 = styled('span')({
  whiteSpace: `pre-wrap`,
  color: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)`,
  fontStyle: `normal`,
  fontFamily: `Poppins`,
  fontWeight: `400`,
  fontSize: `18px`,
  letterSpacing: `0px`,
  textDecoration: `none`,
  textTransform: `none`,
});

const AccountRequest = styled('div')({
  textAlign: `left`,
  whiteSpace: `pre-wrap`,
  fontSynthesis: `none`,
  color: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)`,
  fontStyle: `normal`,
  fontFamily: `Poppins`,
  fontWeight: `400`,
  fontSize: `nullpx`,
  letterSpacing: `NaNpx`,
  textDecoration: `none`,
  textTransform: `none`,
  position: `absolute`,
  left: `112px`,
  top: `117px`,
});

export default Login;
